# Demo API

A small FastAPI service — 3 endpoints, 5 tests. Built as Week 5
of my Get Hired in 6 Months journey.

## Endpoints

| Method | Path | What it does |
|--------|------|--------------|
| GET | /health | Liveness check — returns 200 + status |
| GET | /regions | Lists all AWS regions EC2 runs in |
| GET | /tokens?length=N | Returns a URL-safe random token (8-128 chars) |

## Run locally

```bash
python3 -m venv .venv && source .venv/bin/activate
pip install -r requirements.txt
uvicorn main:app --reload --port 8080
```

Open http://localhost:8080/docs for auto-generated Swagger UI.

## Tests

```bash
pytest -v
```

